Sena! Are you okay?

299
00:13:30,708 --> 00:13:32,208
I didn't feel a thing.

300
00:13:32,291 --> 00:13:34,875
The problem is, I lost almost
half of my battle points.

301
00:13:34,958 --> 00:13:36,083
That's why we brought
a healer with us,

302
00:13:36,166 --> 00:13:37,291
where is she?

303
00:13:37,375 --> 00:13:38,666
Maria!

304
00:13:40,166 --> 00:13:42,541
Maria! What's wrong?

305
00:13:42,625 --> 00:13:45,000
Wait a minute, something
isn't right about this!

306
00:13:48,625 --> 00:13:50,958
Yeah, Rika thinks she
fell asleep on the couch.

307
00:13:54,083 --> 00:13:55,583
That girl is
completely useless.

308
00:13:55,666 --> 00:13:56,666
I don't blame her,
the Prince of Darkness

309
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,208
is pretty boring;

310
00:13:58,291 --> 00:13:59,125
I think a nap
sounds really nice.

311
00:13:59,208 --> 00:14:00,541
You guys!

312
