315
00:14:05,541 --> 00:14:07,375
Well what do you think
Sena are you game?

316
00:14:07,458 --> 00:14:09,583
Oh, I'm all over it!

317
00:14:09,666 --> 00:14:11,041
Blasting hammer!

318
00:14:11,125 --> 00:14:13,375
Here I come!

319
00:14:13,458 --> 00:14:14,500
Do it now!

320
00:14:14,583 --> 00:14:16,375
Yozora!

321
00:14:16,458 --> 00:14:19,041
These wall graphics look
totally realistic don't they?

322
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:22,041
Hey, what the--

323
00:14:23,916 --> 00:14:25,958
That's gotta hurt.

324
00:14:27,708 --> 00:14:29,208
She's dead.

325
