Hey, don't get mad at me,
all I did was say

326
00:14:30,666 --> 00:14:32,583
I could nullify its
attack in theory.

327
00:14:32,666 --> 00:14:33,875
I never said
I was actually

328
00:14:33,958 --> 00:14:35,000
going to go
through with it.

329
00:14:35,083 --> 00:14:36,708
