Rose Guard!

335
00:14:54,208 --> 00:14:55,583
All right, way to go!

336
00:14:55,666 --> 00:14:57,833
I hope it works before
I run outta juice!

337
00:14:57,916 --> 00:14:59,791
Yukimura, Rika, while I'm
holding this thing off,

338
00:14:59,875 --> 00:15:02,291
