-Okay, sounds good!

340
00:15:23,666 --> 00:15:25,916
Rose guard!

341
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,166
What's wrong?

342
00:15:27,250 --> 00:15:29,041
Hey. What the--

343
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:34,708
Yozora, you okay?

344
00:15:36,875 --> 00:15:38,916
Damn you, Meat. Damn you!

345
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,250
Victory is mine!

346
00:15:40,333 --> 00:15:42,375
That's what you get
for underestimating me!

347
00:15:44,041 --> 00:15:45,250
I see.

348
00:15:45,333 --> 00:15:47,833
She tickled her real
body to distract her.

349
