field of battle like a hero.

350
00:15:57,791 --> 00:16:00,000
You're on your
own now, Kodaka.

351
00:16:00,083 --> 00:16:02,125
Don't leave me. You guys!

352
00:16:06,166 --> 00:16:08,416
Well, it looks like this
is the end of the line.

353
00:16:16,666 --> 00:16:18,625
Big bro!

354
00:16:18,708 --> 00:16:20,166
Maria!

355
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:22,583
Hey when did you wake up?

356
00:16:22,666 --> 00:16:24,583
Are you all right?

357
00:16:24,666 --> 00:16:26,250
Yeah, I'm okay.

358
00:16:26,333 --> 00:16:28,625
-Use your magic to
-Bastard! How dare you?

359
00:16:30,208 --> 00:16:32,250
Messing with my brother
like that was a huge mistake

360
00:16:32,333 --> 00:16:34,333
and I'm gonna make
you pay for it, buddy!

361
00:16:34,416 --> 00:16:36,291
I may look innocent, but
when you mess with my bro,

362
00:16:36,375 --> 00:16:37,625
the gloves come off!

363
00:16:37,708 --> 00:16:39,791
Hey!

364
00:16:39,875 --> 00:16:41,208
