365
00:16:44,291 --> 00:16:46,125
That's it.

366
00:16:46,208 --> 00:16:48,125
The end.

367
00:16:55,166 --> 00:16:56,708
Maria?

368
00:16:58,375 --> 00:17:00,750
Kobato. It's you.

369
00:17:00,833 --> 00:17:02,000
This girl said
she would save you

370
00:17:02,083 --> 00:17:03,500
if it's the
last thing she did.

371
00:17:07,250 --> 00:17:09,041
I figured I'd
come check on you.

372
00:17:09,125 --> 00:17:10,083
And, plus I've always
wanted to know

373
00:17:10,166 --> 00:17:12,125
