so late at night.

374
00:17:12,208 --> 00:17:15,375
But I didn't expect it to be
a video game for little kids!

375
00:17:15,458 --> 00:17:17,833
Are you gonna introduce
us to your friend or what?

376
00:17:17,916 --> 00:17:19,583
How do you know this girl?

377
00:17:19,666 --> 00:17:21,125
