378
00:17:21,208 --> 00:17:23,333
Her name is Kobato, and
she's my little sister.

379
00:17:24,708 --> 00:17:26,083
Come on, there's no way
your little sister

380
00:17:26,166 --> 00:17:27,583
could be this cute!

381
00:17:27,666 --> 00:17:28,916
Hey, that's mean!

382
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,541
So what's going on?

383
00:17:30,625 --> 00:17:32,375
Why did you decide
to come here?

384
00:17:32,458 --> 00:17:34,666
Well, big brother, I'm
glad you asked that.

385
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:35,791
Lately, you've been
neglecting me

386
00:17:35,875 --> 00:17:37,208
and spending all
your time hanging out

387
00:17:37,291 --> 00:17:39,208
with this bunch
of idiotic mortals.

388
00:17:39,291 --> 00:17:40,291
So I've come here
because it's obvious

389
00:17:40,375 --> 00:17:41,666
you need supervision.

390
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:43,416
So basically, you're
upset because you feel

391
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:45,458
your brother has put the club
before your relationship,

392
00:17:45,541 --> 00:17:47,583
so you wanted to drop
by and check it out.

393
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:48,666
Is that about right?

394
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:49,958
No. Not at all!

395
00:17:50,041 --> 00:17:52,083
This girl has a
brother complex!

396
00:17:52,166 --> 00:17:53,958
But I can't decide if I
should hate her or not

397
00:17:54,041 --> 00:17:56,000
because she's so
darn adorable!

398
00:17:56,083 --> 00:17:58,666
