how cute she is, it's creepy.

399
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:00,333
Listen.

400
00:18:00,416 --> 00:18:02,500
I'm sorry I've been coming
home so late all the time.

401
00:18:02,583 --> 00:18:03,791
I know!

402
00:18:03,875 --> 00:18:05,458
How bout, from now on, I
make some pork bone ramen

