make it up to you?

404
00:18:07,708 --> 00:18:09,708
Are you serious?
You'd do that?

405
00:18:09,791 --> 00:18:12,000
Will you make it with extra
garlic the way I like it?

406
00:18:12,083 --> 00:18:13,333
Sure, why not?

407
00:18:13,416 --> 00:18:14,708
Yay!

408
00:18:14,791 --> 00:18:16,708
Plus, it's my day off,
so I'll be able to get some

409
00:18:16,791 --> 00:18:18,291
serious cooking
done for once.

410
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:21,083
I can also make
you some lunch.

411
00:18:21,166 --> 00:18:22,708
You're good at that.

412
00:18:22,791 --> 00:18:24,375
Big bro!

413
00:18:27,166 --> 00:18:29,250
Did you defeat the Prince
of Darkness or what?

414
00:18:29,333 --> 00:18:30,416
I'm so glad you're safe!

415
00:18:31,916 --> 00:18:34,166
What's gotten into you,
are you talking in your sleep?

416
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:36,083
I'm wide-awake now.

417
00:18:36,166 --> 00:18:38,291
That game didn't
last very long.

418
00:18:38,375 --> 00:18:40,625
I'm so sorry, Big Brother,
I wanted to protect you

419
00:18:40,708 --> 00:18:43,291
from danger but I drifted
off during the game!

420
00:18:43,375 --> 00:18:44,583
Shut up!

421
00:18:44,666 --> 00:18:45,916
Dummy!

422
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,125
Jerk face!

423
00:18:47,208 --> 00:18:50,333
Weirdo! You big stupid head!

424
00:18:50,416 --> 00:18:51,875
Haven't you ever heard
it's not nice to call

425
00:18:51,958 --> 00:18:53,750
people names
like that, moron?

426
00:18:53,833 --> 00:18:55,000
Shut up, you idiot!

427
00:18:55,083 --> 00:18:56,416
Who the heck do
you think you are?

428
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:57,625
It's her.

429
00:18:57,708 --> 00:19:00,041
My sister, Kobato.

430
00:19:00,125 --> 00:19:02,208
Wait a sec, this is
really your little sis?

431
00:19:02,291 --> 00:19:04,416
Would you please
stop calling me that?

432
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:07,541
I am big.

433
00:19:07,625 --> 00:19:09,291
I have not been
little for years.

434
00:19:09,375 --> 00:19:11,875
Well. Is she your
sister or not?

435
00:19:11,958 --> 00:19:12,875
She's my sister.

436
00:19:12,958 --> 00:19:14,541
He says you are.

437
00:19:14,625 --> 00:19:16,333
I'm a member of the Night Tribe
and have lived among humans

438
00:19:16,416 --> 00:19:18,083
for thousands of years.

439
00:19:18,166 --> 00:19:19,875
My kind has been
at war with you

440
00:19:19,958 --> 00:19:21,083
self-righteous Church dogs

441
00:19:21,166 --> 00:19:23,000
for as long as
I can remember.

442
00:19:23,083 --> 00:19:25,000
They call us 'vampires'
and we strike terror

443
00:19:25,083 --> 00:19:27,375
into the hearts and minds
of people everywhere.

444
00:19:27,458 --> 00:19:28,833
A vampire!

445
00:19:28,916 --> 00:19:30,625
Yes I'm familiar
with your breed!

446
00:19:30,708 --> 00:19:33,041
Tell me, what is a
vampire doing here?

447
00:19:33,125 --> 00:19:35,291
I've come here to keep
my brother away from you.

448
00:19:35,375 --> 00:19:36,666
So his mind isn't poisoned

449
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,416
by a villainous
member of the Church!

450
00:19:41,041 --> 00:19:43,458
On second thought, perhaps
it wouldn't be a bad idea

451
00:19:43,541 --> 00:19:44,916
to join your little club.

452
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,625
