from joining up with a club.

455
00:19:51,833 --> 00:19:53,958
Yeah. Since she's your little
sister, it should be fine.

456
00:19:54,041 --> 00:19:55,291
-Huh?
-She's in.

457
00:19:55,375 --> 00:19:58,166
Plus it seems pretty
clear she has no friends.

458
00:19:58,250 --> 00:20:01,041
Whaddaya say, you
wanna join our club?

459
00:20:01,125 --> 00:20:02,958
The only true friend
I've ever had is

460
00:20:03,041 --> 00:20:04,791
the bitter darkness
of the night.

461
00:20:04,875 --> 00:20:07,500
You're right; she definitely
doesn't have any friends.

462
00:20:07,583 --> 00:20:09,791
Someone wanna tell me why
we're letting a vampire in?

463
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:11,500
My vote's a definite 'no!'

464
00:20:11,583 --> 00:20:14,375
If you so much as touch
a hair on his head, I swear--

465
00:20:14,458 --> 00:20:16,375
He is an apostle of God
who makes me delicious lunches,

466
00:20:16,458 --> 00:20:19,625
and If I so please, I'll
touch every hair on his head!

467
00:20:19,708 --> 00:20:21,583
Time for you to die!

468
00:20:21,666 --> 00:20:23,916
In the name of all that's
holy, I render judgment on you!

469
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,083
Wrong church lady, you're
the one who will shrink

470
00:20:26,166 --> 00:20:27,625
before my dark magic.

471
00:20:27,708 --> 00:20:29,916
My darkness is so powerful
it once made a school classroom

472
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,083
rip right in half!

473
00:20:32,833 --> 00:20:34,500
How do you like this?

474
00:20:34,583 --> 00:20:35,666
How bout that?

475
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:36,750
Your power is weak!

476
00:20:36,833 --> 00:20:38,041
I'll show you weak!

477
00:20:38,125 --> 00:20:39,541
Yikes!

478
00:20:39,625 --> 00:20:41,500
Oh boy.

479
00:20:41,583 --> 00:20:44,875
I really do wish
they'd cut it out already!

480
00:20:44,958 --> 00:20:47,416
I mean it,
I said let me go!

481
00:20:48,791 --> 00:20:49,958
What do you think?

482
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:51,125
Want to clean up?

483
00:20:53,166 --> 00:20:54,333
You know what guys?

484
00:20:54,416 --> 00:20:56,583
I don't think that
game had a point.

485
00:20:56,666 --> 00:20:59,166
What? If you had just watched
out for me back there,

486
00:20:59,250 --> 00:21:01,416
that Prince of Darkness
would have been dead by now.

487
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,875
Well, if you
had been useful

488
00:21:02,958 --> 00:21:04,166
we might have
let you stick around.

489
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:05,625
What did you
just say to me?

490
00:21:05,708 --> 00:21:07,583
I'm saying you need to
learn a little more skill

491
00:21:07,666 --> 00:21:09,625
They sound like your
sister and Maria.

492
00:21:09,708 --> 00:21:10,708
-Weird.
-Yeah.

493
00:21:10,791 --> 00:21:12,125
They sure do.

494
00:21:12,208 --> 00:21:13,541
I guess the lesson here is
that we shouldn't let them

495
00:21:13,625 --> 00:21:15,083
play video games together.

496
00:21:15,166 --> 00:21:16,208
That's too bad.

497
00:21:16,291 --> 00:21:19,125
Rika had a really
great time!

498
00:21:19,208 --> 00:21:20,541
It was the first time Rika
ever played a game

499
00:21:20,625 --> 00:21:22,083
with other people.

500
00:21:22,166 --> 00:21:24,833
That's the most
fun she's ever had.

501
00:21:24,916 --> 00:21:25,875
You really outta
go to a doctor

502
00:21:25,958 --> 00:21:27,166
and get that checked out.

503
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:29,083
Ha, ha, ha!

504
00:21:37,541 --> 00:21:39,125
Oh, Yozora!

505
00:21:39,208 --> 00:21:41,833
Rika forgot to tell you your
outfit earlier was so cute!

506
00:21:41,916 --> 00:21:43,541
Rika's totally crushing.

507
00:21:43,625 --> 00:21:46,583
Hey! Don't tell
me that! It's weird!

508
00:21:46,666 --> 00:21:47,958
Rose Girl.

509
00:21:48,041 --> 00:21:49,916
-She's super cute!
-Stop!

510
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:52,000
I promise you this Jugs,
I'll make you sorry

511
00:21:52,083 --> 00:21:53,125
you ever called me that!

512
00:22:16,666 --> 00:22:18,416
I love you.

